data.description: Charming 1945 home which has been COMPLETLELY remodeled - ALL NEW foundation, plumbing, electrical, energy efficient windows, metal roof, flooring, appliances, kitchen counters & cabinets, HVAC, interior paint, Hardi board siding, new improved circle drive & fenced bachyard. Home is in very nice neighborhood on corner lot. Conveniently located near shopping, schools, medical facilities and I-35 making Dallas, Ft Worth & Waco less than an hour away. The new open concept floor plan makes this home very desirable & a must see home. Wonderful home for a young growing family or a retired couple looking for a very low maintenance home in a relaxing area. Call today & allow us to show you this exciting like new home.
